cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.LG 

The paper discusses privacy threats related to vehicle maneuver data and proposes a driving data analytic engine that can fingerprint the driver using IMUs data. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as it deals with privacy invasion/leakage. The paper also involves data analytics (cs.SI) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) as it deals with vehicle maneuver data and IMUs. Additionally, the paper discusses the implications of driver fingerprinting on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and machine learning (cs.LG).
